{"tid":1818268,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實係咪有人唔知微辣係拎紅色資金嚟香港拓展市場？","createTime":"2020-01-09T18:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T22:11:27.000Z","uid":345528,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"006a7ab3953fc1ec98836f07122229a08dbe17c5","tid":1818268,"uid":345528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:27:07.000Z","msg":"來源：<a href=\"http://www.fic.gov.mo/current/status.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fic.gov.mo%2Fcurrent%2Fstatus.aspx&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdDBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=f0b7c5d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fic.gov.mo/current/status.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n微辣文化有限公司喺2017年向澳門政府申請補貼，項目名為 &ldquo;大灣區進駐計劃（香港）&rdquo;及&ldquo;「微辣」網絡影音製作及器材設備購買&rdquo;，最後拎咗澳門文化產業基金四百萬無償補貼及五百萬免息貸款。<br />\n<br />\n之後佢哋先喺香港開始出名，時間點好吻合。注意，拎咗文化產業基金錢的，就要受澳門政府監察。Especially，<br />\n<br />\n1. 微辣要每6個月/1年向澳門政府交報告<br />\n2. &ldquo;基金會派員作項目查訪&rdquo;，仲有權&ldquo;監督糾正&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"http://www.fic.gov.mo/current/subpage.aspx?a_id=1508917375\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fic.gov.mo%2Fcurrent%2Fsubpage.aspx%3Fa_id%3D1508917375&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdDBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=65dd605a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fic.gov.mo/current/subpage.aspx?a_id=1508917375</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">總之，佢哋長年兒以來都係拎紅色資金，一面同澳門政府講香港係大灣區，一面喺大部分係黃色的香港Generation Y/Z身上獲利。</span>"},{"pid":"902f6e2a3766c2493bbbb69fbe1c8c41ddb0a26d","tid":1818268,"uid":343361,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:28:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><br />\n兩家茶禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"1b388e982c2029ae63a5c2ca1f779a695d6e3726","tid":1818268,"uid":128569,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:31:14.000Z","msg":"好老實講 好多人都係拎緊政府錢 咁又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25210a7f22825e501ad36857e00e601b8fd1b215","tid":1818268,"uid":33999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:32:19.000Z","msg":"我又覺得影響唔大<br />\n你問匯豐中銀做按揭係咪又叫做拎咗紅色資本改善生活？"},{"pid":"177b27ef91dd5bdc23ae238cece10e6517d9cd24","tid":1818268,"uid":20197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1b388e982c2029ae63a5c2ca1f779a695d6e3726","tid":1818268,"uid":128569,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:31:14.000Z","msg":"好老實講 好多人都係拎緊政府錢 咁又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:36:21.000Z","msg":"如果拎政府錢做大黃圈個餅，係好事黎"},{"pid":"c507cf0badb8b6d845535d9dbd6664d1a39e04b7","tid":1818268,"uid":10682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:42:27.000Z","msg":"拎政府錢黎娛樂後生仔唔係仲好咩<br />\n佢地又冇好似tvb咁維穩"},{"pid":"60737c4f1a7b9510a47e137de46851cde5fd78cb","tid":1818268,"uid":144522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:44:29.000Z","msg":"P <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecda8ed31ddcc0ba525cee85a886212d25d0710d","tid":1818268,"uid":345528,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1b388e982c2029ae63a5c2ca1f779a695d6e3726","tid":1818268,"uid":128569,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:31:14.000Z","msg":"好老實講 好多人都係拎緊政府錢 咁又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:51:02.000Z","msg":"拎政府錢同拎政府錢做文宣係兩回事。最近逼得佢哋緊佢哋先被迫以個人名義po兩張黃色的相。<br />\n<br />\n澳門政府文化產業基金批錢係好睇你&ldquo;政治正唔正確&rdquo;，呢樣係係人都知嘅事，特別係喺澳門住得耐嘅人最清楚。而且對於微辣嚟講，即使文化產業基金唔開聲，佢哋自己都應該知道絕對唔可以得失文化局同埋澳門嘅藍色商業圈，<strong>否則，for example，以後仲點可以喺巴士廣告等等地方出現？（只是個例子）</strong><br />\n<br />\n無記錯，澳門政府本身都有額外搵佢哋做過巴士廣告，相信嚟類型嘅廣告係佢哋好重要嘅收入來源。<br />\n<br />\n題外：澳門巴士電視廣告大多由MOME營運，而MOME同澳門通係同一集團，而澳門通同支付寶合作關係好明顯係非常密切。"},{"pid":"3a9e5e2ba9fb6806170a19689e5cf7423642b576","tid":1818268,"uid":345528,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T19:01:53.000Z","msg":"Bottom line 都係，個人覺得如果食肆拎政府錢冇問題，其他嘢拎政府錢都冇問題，但係網媒我就比較難接受。網媒拎咗公權力，受住公權力嘅審查，在社會公義嘅表態上由六月到現在都&ldquo;支支吾吾&rdquo;，就更加接受唔到。"},{"pid":"7e6c3bf4075b5da08db8986dea77e3d3c8eb721c","tid":1818268,"uid":212884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecda8ed31ddcc0ba525cee85a886212d25d0710d","tid":1818268,"uid":345528,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1b388e982c2029ae63a5c2ca1f779a695d6e3726","tid":1818268,"uid":128569,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:31:14.000Z","msg":"好老實講 好多人都係拎緊政府錢 咁又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:51:02.000Z","msg":"拎政府錢同拎政府錢做文宣係兩回事。最近逼得佢哋緊佢哋先被迫以個人名義po兩張黃色的相。<br />\n<br />\n澳門政府文化產業基金批錢係好睇你&ldquo;政治正唔正確&rdquo;，呢樣係係人都知嘅事，特別係喺澳門住得耐嘅人最清楚。而且對於微辣嚟講，即使文化產業基金唔開聲，佢哋自己都應該知道絕對唔可以得失文化局同埋澳門嘅藍色商業圈，<strong>否則，for example，以後仲點可以喺巴士廣告等等地方出現？（只是個例子）</strong><br />\n<br />\n無記錯，澳門政府本身都有額外搵佢哋做過巴士廣告，相信嚟類型嘅廣告係佢哋好重要嘅收入來源。<br />\n<br />\n題外：澳門巴士電視廣告大多由MOME營運，而MOME同澳門通係同一集團，而澳門通同支付寶合作關係好明顯係非常密切。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T21:56:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最近逼得佢哋緊佢哋先被迫以個人名義po兩張黃色的相。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔該做足功課先黎分化得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088170592fa1462e8316b5a00069cf87eda8ad5d","tid":1818268,"uid":96743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"006a7ab3953fc1ec98836f07122229a08dbe17c5","tid":1818268,"uid":345528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:27:07.000Z","msg":"來源：<a href=\"http://www.fic.gov.mo/current/status.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fic.gov.mo%2Fcurrent%2Fstatus.aspx&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdDBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=f0b7c5d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fic.gov.mo/current/status.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n微辣文化有限公司喺2017年向澳門政府申請補貼，項目名為 &ldquo;大灣區進駐計劃（香港）&rdquo;及&ldquo;「微辣」網絡